  "title": "Default style: no default style for Highlight or Hits",
  "body": "It's a bug.\r\n\r\n**What is the current behavior?**\r\nRight now, it applies the default style of the browser even when using itemComponent option.\r\n\r\n![screenshot 2016-12-07 11 40 41](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/393765/20964501/1395e776-bc72-11e6-8b37-274c2606621f.png)\r\n\r\n**What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nIt should apply at least:\r\n - the same font as the widgets\r\n - a proper style for highlight",
